This package has VyOS UDP Broadcast Packet Relay configuration templates and
scripts.

Available configuration nodes:

bcast-relay {
    id 1 {
        description "Foo"
            interface eth1
            interface eth2
            interface eth3
            port 1900
    }
    id 2 {
        description "Bar"
            interface eth1
            interface eth3
            port 6969
    }
}

Source and configuration files/scripts have been aggregated from:
  * https://github.com/nomeata/udp-broadcast-relay/
  * https://github.com/britannic/ubnt-bcast-relay

  Thank you Guys!
